---
// ProcessSection.astro - Explicación del proceso de creación de página webs
---

<section id="process" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Nuestro Proceso Simple y Eficiente</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          En Fazil, hemos optimizado el proceso de creación de páginas web para ofrecerte un resultado profesional en tiempo récord.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Pasos del Proceso -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Paso 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
          <!-- Número de paso con efecto hover -->
          <div class="absolute -right-6 -top-6 bg-primary/10 w-24 h-24 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-4xl text-primary opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity">
            1
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Completa el Formulario</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Llena nuestro formulario detallado con toda la información sobre tu negocio, servicios y preferencias de diseño.
            </p>
            
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Información básica de la empresa</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Detalles de tus servicios o productos</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Preferencias estéticas y visuales</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Paso 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
          <!-- Número de paso con efecto hover -->
          <div class="absolute -right-6 -top-6 bg-primary/10 w-24 h-24 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-4xl text-primary opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity">
            2
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Realiza el Pago</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Realiza el pago de <span class="line-through text-gray-400">$250,000</span> <span class="text-rose-600 font-medium">$190,000</span> a través de nuestros métodos seguros.
            </p>
            
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Transferencia bancaria</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Pagos con tarjeta</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Métodos de pago local</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Paso 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
          <!-- Número de paso con efecto hover -->
          <div class="absolute -right-6 -top-6 bg-primary/10 w-24 h-24 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-4xl text-primary opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity">
            3
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Recibe tu Wireframe</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Inmediatamente después del pago, recibirás un wireframe de tu Pagina Web para tu aprobación.
            </p>
            
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Estructura de la página</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Disposición de elementos</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Esquema básico de diseño</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Paso 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
          <!-- Número de paso con efecto hover -->
          <div class="absolute -right-6 -top-6 bg-primary/10 w-24 h-24 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-4xl text-primary opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity">
            4
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Obtén tu Página</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              En solo 50 minutos después de aprobar el wireframe, tu página web estará lista y en línea.
            </p>
            
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Página completamente funcional</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Hosting gratuito permanente</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Optimización SEO incluida</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Características adicionales del proceso -->
      <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Característica 1 -->
        <div class="bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-lg flex items-start">
          <div class="mr-4 mt-1 bg-primary/10 rounded-full p-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Entrega ultrarrápida</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Tu página web lista en solo 50 minutos después de la aprobación del wireframe. Sin esperas innecesarias.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Característica 2 -->
        <div class="bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-lg flex items-start">
          <div class="mr-4 mt-1 bg-primary/10 rounded-full p-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Proceso optimizado</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Nuestro sistema está diseñado para transformar tus requisitos en una página web profesional de manera eficiente.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Característica 3 -->
        <div class="bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-lg flex items-start">
          <div class="mr-4 mt-1 bg-primary/10 rounded-full p-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Resultados garantizados</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">El servicio incluye una corrección sin costo adicional para asegurar tu completa satisfacción con el resultado final.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Llamada a la acción -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a 
          href="https://wa.me/+573181123660?text=Hola%20Fazil,%20me%20interesa%20una%20landing%20page%20por%20$190,000%20y%20quiero%20conocer%20más%20sobre%20el%20proceso"
